  "texts": [
    "We aim to preserve the privacy of sensitive code repositories while effectively enhancing program repair capabilities.",
    "Fine-tuning LLMs for Program RepairExisting Works.",
    "Pre-trained on extensive corpora, LLMs can already achieve remarkable performance without additional training.",
    "For instance, the AlphaRepair framework, introduced by Xia et al. [97], employs a cloze-style technique to generate code patches leveraging the original CodeBERT [19] without fine-tuning, presenting superior performance compared to many state-ofthe-art APR techniques.",
    "Furthermore, Xia et al. [96] performed an extensive investigation into the direct application of various LLM configurations for APR."
  ],
